        <section class="bariatic-cost">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12 text-center">
                        <h2>Cost of Bariatric Surgery in Jaipur</h2>
                        <p>Bariatric surgery cost varies by state and city in India. The cost of the surgery depends on the hospital, the surgeon, and the type of <br> bariatric surgery recommended by the surgeon based on the patient's BMI (body mass index) and health status.</p>
                        <p>The average cost of bariatric surgery in Jaipur is <span>Rs 225,000 to Rs 700,000.</span></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

